      <title>亨特将于 3 月 6 日公布英国预算，保守党推动赠品</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-27/hunt-to-announce-uk-budget-march-6-as-tories-push-for-giveaways</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国财政大臣杰里米·亨特将于 3 月 6 日宣布英国下一份预算，这可能是执政的保守党在大选前宣布赠品的最后机会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-27/hunt-to-announce-uk-budget-march-6-as-tories-push-for-giveaways</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Dec 2023 11:47:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>刚果警方与反对派发生冲突，选举抗议活动变得丑陋</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-27/drc-police-opposition-clash-as-election-protest-turns-ugly</link>
      <description><![CDATA[刚果民主共和国首都的一场小规模选举抗议活动演变成暴力事件，示威者向安全部队投掷石块，安全部队则向他们发射催泪瓦斯，并袭击了反对派总统候选人马丁·法尤鲁的总部。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-27/drc-police-opposition-clash-as-election-protest-turns-ugly</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Dec 2023 11:31:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列对加沙中部和南部发动猛烈袭击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2023-12-27/urgent-israel-launches-heavy-strikes-across-central-and-southern-gaza-after-widening-its-offensive</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加沙地带拉法（美联社）以色列将针对哈马斯的攻势扩大到更多地区，军方在战争初期曾告诉巴勒斯坦人寻求庇护，随后，以色列连夜对加沙中部和南部发动了猛烈袭击，并持续到周三。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2023-12-27/urgent-israel-launches-heavy-strikes-across-central-and-southern-gaza-after-widening-its-offensive</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Dec 2023 11:23:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国部长兼财政卫士朔伊布勒去世，享年 81 岁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-27/schaeuble-who-helped-forge-german-reunification-dies-at-81</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沃尔夫冈·朔伊布勒 (Wolfgang Schaeuble) 去世了，他曾帮助促成德国统一，但在 2000 年被安格拉·默克尔 (Angela Merkel) 推翻党内领导地位，近十年后又重新出任财政上鹰派的财政部长，带领欧洲最大经济体度过欧元危机。他81岁了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-27/schaeuble-who-helped-forge-german-reunification-dies-at-81</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Dec 2023 08:57:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波兰总统否决后提出加薪计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-27/polish-president-proposes-wage-increase-plan-after-veto</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波兰总统安杰伊·杜达 (Andrzej Duda) 在因对公共媒体提供额外援助的争执中否决了政府的法案后，提出了明年提高教师和其他公共部门工作人员工资的立法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-27/polish-president-proposes-wage-increase-plan-after-veto</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Dec 2023 08:33:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
